title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, there is no data returned. The expected behavior is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog. Steps to reproduce: 1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 2. The query result will be stored in the output parameter as an object.
